# {{title_name}}

Simple Telegram bot written in Go with a small production-friendly layout.

## Structure

- `cmd/bot` - application entrypoint
- `internal/app` - bot wiring and update loop
- `internal/config` - environment configuration
- `internal/handlers` - Telegram message handlers
- `internal/state` - per-user state storage
- `pkg/messages` - reusable response text helpers

## Setup

1. Copy `.env.example` to `.env`
2. Fill in `TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN`
3. Run `go mod tidy`
4. Run `go run ./cmd/bot`
